Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君臨破碎的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放的枷鎖啊 何時收緊束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高指令第一話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指令！覺醒吧、惡之力！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 打個比方...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設你能夠實現任何願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會許下什麼願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 想成為歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要錢...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得永恆的生命！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有不同的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對自己來說那一定是幸福的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們的願望從根本上來說總是利己的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的願望才顯得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來輪到你了 映司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...願望是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:01:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映司？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:01:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望是...
